description: Two figures are engaged in excavation, one holding a skull while the other chips at a bone embedded in the earth. The site appears to be rich in ancient remains, including pottery and a bull's skull. Unexpectedly, amidst these artifacts, a modern mailbox is unearthed bearing the names "FRED AND WILMA". This surreal discovery places fictional characters from a prehistoric animated series within a realistic archaeological context, highlighting the absurdity of treating their world as historical fact. The irony lies in the serious scientific approach applied to uncovering relics of a purely imagined existence.
